---
import Section from '../Section.astro';
---

<Section class="py-24 lg:py-40 relative">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-24 items-center">
    
    {/* Left Content */}
    <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col justify-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[var(--text)] mb-6 leading-[1.1]">
        This is <span class="text-[var(--accent)]">not</span> a generic market summary.
      </h1>

      <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-8 max-w-lg">
        A Should-I report is designed to answer one question:
      </p>

      {/* Glassy Quote Block */}
      <blockquote class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-medium text-[var(--text)] bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-md border border-[var(--border)] rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm">
        “If I go ahead with this decision, what am I <span class="italic text-[var(--accent)]">not</span> seeing right now?”
      </blockquote>

      <p class="text-lg text-[var(--text-muted)] mt-8">
        Below are examples of the kinds of insights owners receive.
      </p>
    </div>

    {/* Right Visual (Abstract Iridescent Object) */}
    <div class="relative h-[500px] w-full flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-end">
      {/* CSS-only Abstract Shape Simulation */}
      <div class="relative w-[400px] h-[400px] animate-float">
        {/* Main iridescence */}
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--accent)] via-purple-500 to-pink-500 rounded-[3rem] opacity-80 blur-lg mix-blend-multiply filter"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-4 bg-gradient-to-tl from-blue-400 via-teal-300 to-yellow-200 rounded-[2.5rem] opacity-90 blur-md mix-blend-overlay"></div>
        {/* 'Glass' surface */}
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-[3rem] border border-white/40 shadow-2xl skew-y-3 skew-x-3 rotate-6"></div>
        <div class="absolute -inset-10 bg-[var(--accent)]/20 rounded-full blur-3xl -z-10"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</Section>

<style>
  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-20px) rotate(2deg); }
  }
  .animate-float {
    animation: float 8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
</style>
